Constructor Detail

InMessageNode

public InMessageNode(InMessage message,
                     javax.swing.tree.DefaultTreeModel treeModel)
Creates an InMessage that is a TreeNode and wraps a non-Swing InMessage implementation. The wrapped InMessage contains the logic, this class is simply a wrapper allowing the InMessage to be displayed in a JTree.

Parameters:
message - The Message to wrap. This object may not be an instance of TreeNode.
treeModel - the tree model this node belongs to
